Mxit,is,a,social,networking,application,for,users,in,Africa,Users,of,Mxit,can,share,updates,chat,with,friends,text,message,and,upload,images,and,media,among,other,things,The,Mxit,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,Mxit,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,sending,and,receiving,messages,listing,and,retrieving,elements,and,managing,user,accounts